root: ^How was your time exploring this unkown planet?

c-0: ^The aliens have managed to get away. We have tried to track them all over the galaxy and it seems they have taken their own galaxy quest to discover a new war within the stars.
^Apparently they have tried to take more babies throughout each of the planets.
^This means Joe, unfortunately  we cannot let you continue with your research and missions and we are going to have to take over the investigation.
^We will keep you updated with any developments.

^As we cannot find your old baby, we have a found a new specied of alien for you to look after. It can be known as an E-Wook. They can be angry little creatures so try and be careful looking after it and do not loose this baby in space.
